  "title": "Vanilla Ice Cream",
  "description": "The finest (fully serverside) Vanilla ice cream you will ever taste.",
  "body": "Vanilla Ice Cream modpack aims to enhance and optimize vanilla experience with mods, resource packs and datapacks, while keeping the original <i>vanilla</i> 🍦 feel and being purely server-side. Clients can join your server without even one mod (they will however miss out on some features like trash slot or voice chat).\n<hr>\n<b>This modpack is in beta, expect many changes!</b>\n<p>Java 17 is required!</p>\n<b>Due to technical limitations when creating a world data packs menu must be opened once if you wish to use included ones</b>\n<hr>\n<b>Here are some of this modpacks features:</b>\n<h2><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/simple-voice-chat\">Voice chat</a></h2>\n<img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/68ba387336b6224aebecb712b3e4824a5b5616852bd5f4b010212bc3014b412b/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f5a565366426d732e706e67\" width=\"375\">\n<img src=\"https://camo.githubusercontent.com/5d9a7ab6157974b25b72894392b4ed4e02fdca6e31dea29b5884ac3ea34d65e0/68747470733a2f2f692e696d6775722e636f6d2f544d79665359552e706e67\" width=\"375\">\n<h2><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/brb\">Better Recipe Book</a></h2>\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mrshmllow/BetterRecipeBook/1.17/.github/images/demo_brewing_recipe_book.png\" width=\"350\">\n<img src=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/mrshmllow/BetterRecipeBook/1.17/.github/images/demo_centered_inventory.png\" width=\"400\">\n<h2><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/repurposed-structures-fabric/screenshots\">More vanilla structures variants</a></h2>\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/300/593/2020-03-18_18.png\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/341/538/2021-02-16_10.png\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://media.forgecdn.net/attachments/423/494/overworldcity2.png\" width=\"280\">\n<h2><a href=\"https://modrinth.com/mod/towns-and-towers-structure-add-on\">New villages and pillager outposts variants</a></h2>\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DjLobEOy/images/836fc38219a15dfef0dd04de74b111ad15a5d00a.png\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DjLobEOy/images/3f1f89dda25672681bbbb58415439c959912bd83.png\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://cdn.modrinth.com/data/DjLobEOy/images/92f557a382c73ed5744b2e3a8900aabf1d1fdcf4.png\" width=\"280\">\n<h2>Shaders support</h2>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/mEFAqkD.png\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/B6d2AZD.jpg\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/67xKZWd.jpg\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/sGA95Ul.jpg\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yIof7Wg.jpg\" width=\"280\">\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/KtfGQY5.jpg\" width=280\">\n<h2>Optimization</h2>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/TzLurlG.png\" width=\"280\">\n<iframe width=\"250\" src=\"https://www.youtube.com/embed/iMg0jRpltXY\"></iframe>\n<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/yCNK602.png\" width=\"300\">\n<hr>\n<p><b>Included mods:</b>\n<li>Check out dependencies in the latest release</li></p>\n<p><b>Included mods outside of modrinth:</b>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/advancement-plaques-fabric\">Advancement Plaques [Fabric]</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/ambient-environment\">Ambient Environment</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/bsasealteam6/AnvilFix\">AnvilFix</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/better-third-person\">Better Third Person</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/controlling\">Controlling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/ChloeDawn/Couplings\">Couplings</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/A5b84/dark-loading-screen\">Dark Loading Screen</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/drp-global-datapack\">Global Packs</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/hwyla-addon-horse-info\">Hwyla Addon Horse Info</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/iceberg-fabric\">Iceberg [Fabric]</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/jamlib\">JamLib</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/mambience\">MAmbience</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/pling\">Pling</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/fantahund/Resolution-Control/tree/1.19\">ResolutionControl+</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/wi-zoom\">WI Zoom</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/xaeros-minimap\">Xaero's Minimap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/mc-mods/xaeros-world-map\">Xaero's World Map</a></li>\n</p>\n<p><b>Included resource packs:</b>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.curseforge.com/minecraft/texture-packs/creative-music\">Creative music</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vanillatweaks.net/picker/resource-packs\">Vanilla Tweaks</a></li>\n</p>\n<p><b>Included data packs:</b>\n<li><a href=\"https://vanillatweaks.net/picker/crafting-tweaks\">Vanilla Tweaks Crafting Tweaks</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://vanillatweaks.net/picker/datapacks\">Vanilla Tweaks Data Packs</a></li></p>\n<p><b>Included shader packs:</b>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.complementary.dev/reimagined/\">Complementary Reimagined</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://www.complementary.dev/shaders-v4/\">Complementary Shaders v4</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/Michael1297/VanillAA-Shaders\">VanillAA</a></li>\n</p>",
